{"tid":1425648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[TLDR] 警察策略分析: 對示威者依舊粗暴，但對街坊開始想扮下好人","createTime":"2019-08-06T19:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:41:08.000Z","uid":161430,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"44cbc43efd163feb10e994692ff3f8ebabd83c36","tid":1425648,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:16:16.000Z","msg":"首先，警察話宜家日日會開記者會 (雖然今日果個已經失敗左)<br />\n<br />\n而後又有今晚行動，警察又刻意對示威者講左句: <span style=\"color: red;\">你地唔好咁嘈 會嘈到街坊</span>之外，佢地仲搵左警隊既<span style=\"color: red;\">傳媒聯絡員</span>出場，着藍色背心呢種<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://www.singpao.com.hk/image_upload/1483904489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Fimage_upload%2F1483904489.jpg&h=7960e8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好明顯佢地策略係對示威者依舊粗暴，但對樓上不知情既街坊，就開始想扮好人拉攏佢地支持自己。<br />\n<br />\n不過由於警察都係智商太低，大量警員最後配合唔倒劇本，都係失常咁樣瘋狂打錯、拉錯街坊，以致扮好人計劃徹底fail左。但係佢地有呢個計劃都係對我地既警號黎。<br />\n<br />\n宜家示威者去到大部分既區，其實周圍都會有街坊，所以示威者一定同樣要討好街坊，呢點真係好重要，<span style=\"color: red;\">呢個唔止係失唔失民心既問題，而係示威者得唔到街坊心，根本就圍唔起警署，一入到社區，周圍既人都變成係敵人，咁樣會大大影響埋示威者既行動。</span><br />\n<br />\n試諗下，如果比警察成功贏到街坊既心，示威者會有幾慘？示威者既然都咁努力，出汗又出錢買gear仲要冒住被捕既風險抗爭，點解要因為一時對街坊唔小心激動左，就令自己處於一個劣勢之中？呢個真係唔關失唔失民心事，而係太唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n其實，前線只係需要<span style=\"color: red;\">做幾樣好簡單既野就可以改變好多野</span>，例如:<br />\n叫街坊 閂窗既時候，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好用打仗tone</span>激動叫人閂窗，可以正常咁講句<span style=\"color: red;\">「麻煩小心安全，閂窗呀唔該」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n因為冇人會想自己住既屋企附近，成日出現好似打仗咁既聲線，佢地好多人，唔會區分示威者係好人定壞人，總之就唔鍾意屋企附近咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，所以示威者亦應該將個波大大力推返去警察度，講聲<span style=\"color: red;\">「大家小心警察同警棍呀 唔該曬 唔好意思佢地又衝入黎喇」。</span><br />\n<br />\n言語間，灌輸比街坊知，你唔鍾意屋企附近咁樣？係警察造成架，唔係示威者造成。<br />\n<br />\n對街坊，你就係要以一個你係好人，幫緊佢既友善冷靜語氣去講野，再用一種見到怪物要跑入黎害村民既口吻，去形容警察。千期唔好大大聲好激動好惡咁講閂窗呀，走啦 etc<br />\n<br />\n最後想講，其實以我實際多次觀察，屌POPO 同 鬧示威者既街坊，大約六四至七三比，屌警察既略多，但話示威者唔岩既都真係有唔少。<br />\n<br />\n而鬧示威者既，佢地好多其實唔係乜野壞人，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家請理解，佢地只係接收既資訊同我地完全唔同</span>，例如即係睇得多cctvb、方向報，所以立場先會唔同，所以雖然警察射曬催淚彈入村，佢地自己明明都硬食一份，但因為已先入為主，誤會<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者先係始作俑者，係班暴徒累到警察要入埋村，所以自己先要食催淚彈</span>，佢地個思維真係咁樣架。<br />\n<br />\n所以以後見到佢地真係有禮貌少少，特別係宜家警察想扮好人就要更加小心。<br />\n<br />\n警察宜家既策略就係對示威者粗暴、賤格，但對街坊就開始扮好人，咁示威者就應該做返一樣既野: 對黑警態度照舊，但對街坊就超級友善。<br />\n<br />\n得街坊得天下呀各位。"},{"pid":"aec60138740608d9f3889afef237642f44650015","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"捉鐳射槍....收左皮啦"},{"pid":"e10d2e899aedd9aaa399bf0cc60c422cb0804ae6","tid":1425648,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n分區行動一定需要得到地區支援"},{"pid":"8c9614679c7d1bf4377504db0f2394119c56a94b","tid":1425648,"uid":168161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心警察啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閂窗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8b28b7e89fc552e3f00983816175f75fd285b6ee","tid":1425648,"uid":161430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"aec60138740608d9f3889afef237642f44650015","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"捉鐳射槍....收左皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:17.000Z","msg":"咁係佢地真係太撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捉埋區議員添"},{"pid":"6cb483b501b83f7a85f1ae3a392821c0eaf1e228","tid":1425648,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aec60138740608d9f3889afef237642f44650015","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"捉鐳射槍....收左皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦一毛，又要狙擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6daf87ca43f5274830b44440b560dbea0a83618","tid":1425648,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:32.000Z","msg":"深水單野都係街坊去先架啦，其它人有撚咁快到場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我覺得地方出事地方解決，又唔係吹大雞"},{"pid":"3547047a5696d3d9f2cc249947f74a4e57dbd550","tid":1425648,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c9614679c7d1bf4377504db0f2394119c56a94b","tid":1425648,"uid":168161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心警察啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閂窗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:21:14.000Z","msg":"冇錯就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我比怪獸追緊 樓上既街坊都要小心佢地"},{"pid":"a94707f721b3391366594e3f0cb2e686a0bf2b32","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6cb483b501b83f7a85f1ae3a392821c0eaf1e228","tid":1425648,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aec60138740608d9f3889afef237642f44650015","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"捉鐳射槍....收左皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦一毛，又要狙擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:21:55.000Z","msg":"屈毛黨你好"},{"pid":"7893046cdf5d9fd855cd31c0eb57e1e54e23f4ec","tid":1425648,"uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d6daf87ca43f5274830b44440b560dbea0a83618","tid":1425648,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:32.000Z","msg":"深水單野都係街坊去先架啦，其它人有撚咁快到場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我覺得地方出事地方解決，又唔係吹大雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:22:22.000Z","msg":"將軍澳 天水圍都係<br />\n放心 我明有好多街坊係支持示威者 多過屌既<br />\n不過如果可以做好少少令其他街坊都connect埋<br />\n以後入到社區贏面更大姐"},{"pid":"cf3c2f7801a8cc7c7236a0bc29a83302503ce7b7","tid":1425648,"uid":40628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:23:08.000Z","msg":"網友：請廣傳前線手足，狗捉人的新招數<br />\n啱啱睇深水埗直播 :　深水埗防暴狗離班街坊二三十米 ， 係街坊入面有幾個手足戴住口罩用雷射照狗，仲同狗對駡咗一陣， 突然成班防暴狗衝埋去，你哋諗下防暴狗拎住個長盾點可能走得快？ 有乜可能捉到人？<br />\n<br />\n但班街坊一散， 已經見到幾個帶口罩嘅手足畀人㩒喺地下。<br />\n最奇怪被圍有個女仔， 身邊企住一個長髮妹， 仲以為個長髮妹係個女仔的朋友，原來係差婆，估計係呢個差婆拉住個女仔等佢走唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n今次黑狗捉人準確率好高，捉嘅個個都係戴口罩揹背囊，冇一個似街坊。 <br />\n<br />\n咁推斷一早有便衣狗埋伏係街坊入面，仲要企近帶口罩嘅手足。防暴狗一沖埋嚟， 街坊會驚慌散開，便衣狗就拉住手足等輕裝的防暴狗趕嚟拉人。<br />\n<br />\n所以各位手足要注意，就算你哋企喺一大班街坊裏面，一定要離開狗防線有一定距離，最少50米，仲要留意你身邊有冇便衣狗扮的假街坊。<br />\n請小心，因為黑警這行動絕對是送彈藥給左膠"},{"pid":"53e724592e84e48848699b65384106340442061e","tid":1425648,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7893046cdf5d9fd855cd31c0eb57e1e54e23f4ec","tid":1425648,"uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d6daf87ca43f5274830b44440b560dbea0a83618","tid":1425648,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:32.000Z","msg":"深水單野都係街坊去先架啦，其它人有撚咁快到場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我覺得地方出事地方解決，又唔係吹大雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:22:22.000Z","msg":"將軍澳 天水圍都係<br />\n放心 我明有好多街坊係支持示威者 多過屌既<br />\n不過如果可以做好少少令其他街坊都connect埋<br />\n以後入到社區贏面更大姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得比返班街坊自己屌鳩班狗已經夠，等D街坊又食下警棍TG，自自然然多人加入陣營"},{"pid":"39013ebf5c4fa7d1005e817c9c35a01989c682eb","tid":1425648,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:23:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f91b243fdbfaf339b03385c16432e77b3b9f9026","tid":1425648,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:32:27.000Z","msg":"明明串撚到爆 , 乜柒都話幫唔到記者"},{"pid":"e4c8cdd58a45e01eaf3b692160045725f7e8641d","tid":1425648,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a94707f721b3391366594e3f0cb2e686a0bf2b32","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6cb483b501b83f7a85f1ae3a392821c0eaf1e228","tid":1425648,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aec60138740608d9f3889afef237642f44650015","tid":1425648,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:18:43.000Z","msg":"捉鐳射槍....收左皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦一毛，又要狙擊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:21:55.000Z","msg":"屈毛黨你好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:37:10.000Z","msg":"維穩紀錄真係水洗都唔清，起底就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近鄰國經濟差，小心再扣人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335a1b4593f004a467bc8adb02c47d68e7adbd7e","tid":1425648,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:41:37.000Z","msg":"班狗打公關牌只會弄巧反拙，仲記得之前屈示威者唔俾救援員救人，仲被爆濫用救護車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打晚再打公關牌，結果辣興班深水埗街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我地再有禮貌少少，每日記者會都救唔到班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b838258e9366f870087277c4dfd88f71045b8d05","tid":1425648,"uid":93660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"g持！"},{"pid":"a5a44679a9d8e154cd4a270d2ded730e27a2a242","tid":1425648,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4284c6d233742c6ca6698b4aac7173f5fc0431a9","tid":1425648,"uid":291203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"劇本好好，但隊友係豬<br />\n<br />\n啊，唔係，係連狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}